</p>
<p>
Yeah, I'm beginning to think all that power is starting to go to her head. 
</p>
<p>
"You said it, dude.  She <em>is</em> pretty hot, though." 
</p>
<p>
Well, yeah, a +22 total bonus to CHA will do that.  Which reminds me, we've got skill points to allocate:  1 to Bearform-combat, 1 to Temporal and 3 to Spell-power.  My unhasted speed in bear form drops to -14, but Essence of Speed is up to spell effect level 54, so my top speed stays at +26.  Say, as long as we're in Gondolin, maybe we should do the house quest here. 
</p>
<p>
"Dude, <em>another</em> house?" 
</p>
<p>
Well, the others <em>are</em> getting kinda full.  <em>[checks notes]</em>  Hmm, no, we need to prepare for this one. 
