From here we head to: 
</p>
<p>
<strong>Bree</strong> 
</p>
<p>
to sell off the randart Morning Star and stow the randart Ring Mail.  As long as I'm in the neighborhood, I think I'll take a side trip to Khazad-dum.  On the way, I encounter another odd vaultish thing on MoM 50, this one looking like it was carved straight out of the mountains: 
