</p>
<p>
"Whoa.  So, how do you identify the liquid?" 
</p>
<p>
You fill a bottle with it and identify the potion. 
</p>
<p>
"Oh, I get it.  There's some potion things you want a lot of, so you're gonna go find a fountain of &#8216;em and fill up a lot of bottles." 
