<img src="./wiki/classic/img/biggrin.png" alt=":D" height="15" width="15"> <img src="./wiki/classic/img/biggrin.png" alt=":D" height="15" width="15"> I think that last one plugs one of the holes I was having problems with before.  Lemme go back to my equipment optimizer&#8230; 
